WEBVTT

00:01.401 --> 00:03.635
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da,
ba-da-ba-da-ba ♪

00:03.670 --> 00:05.137
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da ♪
Let's go!

00:05.172 --> 00:06.838
♪ We'll be there ♪

00:06.873 --> 00:09.508
♪ A wink and a smile
and a great old time ♪

00:09.543 --> 00:11.710
♪ Yeah, we'll be there ♪

00:11.745 --> 00:13.812
♪ Wherever we are,
there's some fun to be found ♪

00:13.847 --> 00:16.148
♪ We'll be there
when you turn that corner ♪

00:16.183 --> 00:17.482
♪ We'll jump out the bush ♪

00:17.517 --> 00:19.184
♪ With a big bear hug
and a smile ♪

00:19.219 --> 00:20.619
♪ We'll be there ♪

00:22.722 --> 00:24.890
♪♪

00:26.760 --> 00:30.028
So...tell me, again,
in your own words --

00:30.063 --> 00:32.664
why are you here today
in anger management?

00:32.699 --> 00:34.199
Hmm, what am I
doing here again?

00:34.234 --> 00:35.567
You're my agent --

00:35.602 --> 00:37.235
why'd you book this
complete waste of time?

00:37.270 --> 00:41.073
All of your engagements were
cancelled after...the incident.

00:41.108 --> 00:43.608
OK, shoo, shoo -- that's enough
out of you, thank you.

00:43.643 --> 00:46.778
Ahem. Look, Doc, this is all
really unnecessary.

00:46.813 --> 00:48.747
It was a big misunderstanding!

00:48.782 --> 00:50.849
I-I don't have any anger issues.

00:50.884 --> 00:53.718
Well, it says here,
if you don't complete therapy,

00:53.753 --> 00:56.021
you can't resume
your business activity.

00:56.056 --> 00:58.390
So, why don't we
review the events?

00:58.425 --> 01:00.092
Okay, okay, fine.
Ahem.

01:00.127 --> 01:03.895
So you know that really annoying
megahit kids show, "The Corgis"?

01:03.930 --> 01:08.033
Well, after years of trying,
I finally landed a guest role!

01:08.068 --> 01:09.901
I signed on, and we jumped
into the shoot.

01:09.936 --> 01:13.538
Everything was going great,
until the theme song came on.

01:13.573 --> 01:16.108
♪ Green sandwich ♪

01:16.143 --> 01:18.043
♪ Corgi party ♪

01:18.078 --> 01:19.978
♪ Red pineapple ♪

01:20.013 --> 01:21.613
♪ Corgi party ♪

01:21.648 --> 01:23.215
♪ Blue banana ♪

01:23.250 --> 01:24.549
Man: Cut, cut cut cut.

01:24.584 --> 01:26.051
This isn't gonna work, Nom Nom.

01:26.086 --> 01:28.487
We need stacks more smiles --
heaps of it!

01:28.522 --> 01:30.722
But I've been smiling
this whole time.

01:30.757 --> 01:32.791
Yeah, but nah.
give us a big smile!

01:32.826 --> 01:35.660
Yeah, mate! Let's get in there
and see some pearly whites!

01:35.695 --> 01:38.063
Man: All right!
Camera's loaded, let's shoot.

01:38.098 --> 01:39.731
Everyone, places.

01:39.766 --> 01:42.000
Nom Nom: And it kept going,
take after take, cut after cut,

01:42.035 --> 01:44.336
never-ending smiles,
and it was too much!!

01:44.371 --> 01:46.338
Aah!

01:46.373 --> 01:48.173
Stupid song!
- Crikey!

01:48.208 --> 01:49.608
Aah!

01:49.643 --> 01:51.309
Hey!
Call the coppers!

01:51.344 --> 01:52.911
Grah!

01:52.946 --> 01:54.279
Noms, are you --

01:54.314 --> 01:56.281
Aah!
- Run for it!

01:56.316 --> 01:57.482
Aah!

01:57.517 --> 01:58.917
[ Screaming ]

01:58.952 --> 02:01.319
I might have overreacted
a little bit,

02:01.354 --> 02:03.155
but the truth was grossly
exaggerated.

02:03.190 --> 02:04.456
Pleh.

02:04.491 --> 02:06.124
I'm sorry,
but you can't resume

02:06.159 --> 02:08.660
until you've completed
some sort of therapy.

02:08.695 --> 02:10.462
And we've run
out of options.

02:10.497 --> 02:11.830
So your agent and I

02:11.865 --> 02:13.632
thought it was best to bring
in a specialist.

02:13.667 --> 02:15.133
[ Scoffs ] Give me a break.

02:15.168 --> 02:17.802
Someone who specializes
in being happy.

02:17.837 --> 02:19.504
You can come in now, sir.

02:19.539 --> 02:21.640
Uh, hello?
Ah! Nom Nom!

02:21.675 --> 02:23.808
Oh, it's been ages, man!

02:23.843 --> 02:25.043
No! No!

02:25.078 --> 02:27.112
No! No! No! No way! No!

02:27.147 --> 02:29.281
You! This was your doing!

02:29.316 --> 02:30.849
No! No! No! No! No!

02:30.884 --> 02:33.952
Aw, he's so excited!
I missed you too, Nom Nom!

02:33.987 --> 02:36.154
No, get out of here!
Nobody wants you!

02:36.189 --> 02:38.690
-Now, Nom Nom --
-No! Don't tell me what to do!

02:38.725 --> 02:40.859
Nom Nom, please.
He can guide you.

02:40.894 --> 02:44.129
Let him teach you how to purge
all that negative energy.

02:44.164 --> 02:46.565
I know this is a big step to
repairing our friendship,

02:46.600 --> 02:48.800
so when I heard you needed help,
I couldn't say no!

02:48.835 --> 02:50.802
Please give this a try
Mr. Nom Nom, sir.

02:50.837 --> 02:53.838
Oh, you don't understand!
"The Corgis" aren't worth this!

02:53.873 --> 02:55.540
Wha--
Did you say "The Corgis"?

02:55.575 --> 02:56.908
Ah, I love that show!

02:56.943 --> 02:59.010
The kangaroo's got to be
my favorite in the cast.

02:59.045 --> 03:01.012
I've got a picture
of him right here!

03:01.047 --> 03:03.548
Oh, stop!
Don't you get it?

03:03.583 --> 03:05.183
You bears mess up everything
when you're around.

03:05.218 --> 03:06.651
Especially you, Grizz!

03:06.686 --> 03:09.521
Oh, all right, Nom Nom,
whatever you want.

03:09.556 --> 03:10.855
Wait!
Sir!

03:10.890 --> 03:12.657
Please reconsider, sir.
You need him!

03:12.692 --> 03:14.492
Your popularity ratings
could really use

03:14.527 --> 03:15.994
this boost with
"The Corgis."

03:16.029 --> 03:18.530
Andy Bangs has surpassed you
in search results and views.

03:18.565 --> 03:20.365
And your mansion --
we could lose it!

03:20.400 --> 03:21.700
What? [ Grumbles ]

03:21.735 --> 03:23.935
Okay, okay,
get that out of here.

03:23.970 --> 03:25.203
[ Groans ]

03:25.238 --> 03:27.772
Hey, bud.

03:27.807 --> 03:30.075
I-I was wrong back there.
I know we've had

03:30.110 --> 03:32.777
our differences, but who am I
to deny help from you.

03:32.812 --> 03:34.879
After all,
I could really use it.

03:34.914 --> 03:37.048
You're saying
you'll take my help?

03:37.083 --> 03:38.083
Yes.

03:38.118 --> 03:40.252
Ah! Is this for real?
I'm allowed to help?!

03:40.287 --> 03:41.686
Yep, for realsies.

03:41.721 --> 03:44.356
Whoo-hoo!
I won't let you down!

03:44.391 --> 03:45.690
Sweet.

03:45.725 --> 03:47.726
Step one --
dance yoga!

03:47.761 --> 03:49.628
Here we go,
just follow my lead.

03:49.663 --> 03:52.297
[ Takes deep breath ]
And, up!

03:52.332 --> 03:55.800
Huh! Huh!
Uh, uh! Schooo!

03:55.835 --> 03:57.602
Eating is obviously
therapeutic,

03:57.637 --> 03:59.638
and so is spreading jam
all over a bagel!

03:59.673 --> 04:02.540
Mm, mm, that's good.

04:02.575 --> 04:04.909
Argh!

04:04.944 --> 04:08.480
Drawing cute, happy pictures
always cheers me up!

04:17.290 --> 04:19.324
[ Groans ]

04:19.359 --> 04:22.093
And this is the most important
part -- you got to smile!

04:22.128 --> 04:24.496
Express those bright
emotions outward!

04:24.531 --> 04:26.298
Okay,
give it a try, friend!

04:26.333 --> 04:27.599
Almost got it.

04:27.634 --> 04:29.267
Just a bit more.

04:29.302 --> 04:31.102
Come on now, bigger!

04:31.137 --> 04:32.971
[ Groaning ]

04:33.006 --> 04:34.273
Bigger!

04:36.309 --> 04:38.243
Gah!

04:38.278 --> 04:40.478
Nom Nom, what's --

04:40.513 --> 04:42.447
Aah! Aah!

04:42.482 --> 04:44.316
[ Nom Nom screaming ]

04:47.454 --> 04:49.454
Oh, my gosh, I've never seen him
like this before!

04:49.489 --> 04:50.855
It's like
he's gotten worse!

04:50.890 --> 04:52.590
At this rate,
Nom Nom will be ruined!

04:52.625 --> 04:54.693
We got to calm him down!

04:56.162 --> 04:58.463
Nom Nom!
- Oh, gosh. Please calm down.

04:58.498 --> 04:59.998
You have to stop this!

05:00.033 --> 05:01.499
[ Growling ]

05:01.534 --> 05:03.134
Ah! Now what do I do?

05:03.169 --> 05:05.437
Throw it out the window!
Restrain him!

05:05.472 --> 05:07.138
But how?!

05:07.173 --> 05:10.008
Aah!

05:12.679 --> 05:15.313
Nom Nom?
You okay?

05:15.348 --> 05:17.249
Wha-- Huh?

05:19.185 --> 05:20.952
I'm -- It worked!

05:20.987 --> 05:23.121
Everything
all right, buddy?

05:23.156 --> 05:26.658
Yes. In fact, I've never
felt so peaceful before.

05:26.693 --> 05:28.226
That's so great,
Nom Nom!

05:28.261 --> 05:30.628
You know my plan had some kinks,
but in the end, it worked out!

05:30.663 --> 05:33.164
This...is...a miracle!
We got to celebrate!

05:33.199 --> 05:35.333
Ah! Let me grab some
of those bagels!

05:35.368 --> 05:38.069
Whoa!

05:38.104 --> 05:40.171
[ Growling ]

05:40.206 --> 05:43.342
[ Muffled scream ]

05:46.112 --> 05:47.912
Ha! I feel great!

05:47.947 --> 05:50.181
Agent, call "The Corgis."
I'm ready for the shoot!

05:50.216 --> 05:52.183
And, Grizz,
will you come with me?

05:52.218 --> 05:54.552
Oh, my gosh, you mean I can come
with you to see "The Corgis"!?

05:54.587 --> 05:57.222
Ah, yes! I'm so in!

05:59.893 --> 06:01.726
So, this is where
the magic happens.

06:01.761 --> 06:03.528
Ah! Are the Corgis
here already?

06:03.563 --> 06:04.829
Wow, their fur
is everywhere!

06:04.864 --> 06:06.197
There's even some
on the lights.

06:06.232 --> 06:08.233
Oh, yeah,
that's dangerously hot.

06:08.268 --> 06:09.734
♪ Corgi ♪

06:09.769 --> 06:11.669
No, no, no, no, mate.

06:11.704 --> 06:13.204
♪ Corgi ♪

06:13.239 --> 06:15.573
♪ Corgi ♪
- ♪ Corgi ♪

06:15.608 --> 06:16.775
Hey, here he comes.

06:16.810 --> 06:18.209
Hello, gentlemen.

06:18.244 --> 06:20.111
Thank you for giving me
a second chance at this.

06:20.146 --> 06:22.547
Hey, Noms,
everything all right?

06:22.582 --> 06:24.249
Yeah, all good, mate?
We cool?

06:24.284 --> 06:25.683
[ Laughs ] Yep, I'm cool.

06:25.718 --> 06:28.887
Good, last time we saw ya,
ya ripped Corgi Dan's leg off.

06:28.922 --> 06:30.255
She'll be right.

06:30.290 --> 06:32.957
I assure you, my leg-ripping
days are over.

06:32.992 --> 06:36.060
Yeah, but just in case, we hired
some more security, you know.

06:36.095 --> 06:38.596
Requesting mobile support.

06:38.631 --> 06:41.299
It's fine, 'cause nothing bad's
gonna to happen this time.

06:41.334 --> 06:42.801
Gonna be a bonza day!

06:42.836 --> 06:44.569
Uh, one second?

06:44.604 --> 06:46.471
Oh.

06:46.506 --> 06:48.807
[ Muffled scream ]

06:48.842 --> 06:50.942
Corgi Dan seems
so cool.

06:50.977 --> 06:52.911
All right, camera's loaded.
Let's shoot.

06:52.946 --> 06:54.646
Everyone, places!

06:54.681 --> 06:55.980
Yes! Beautiful smile!

06:56.015 --> 06:57.949
Let's keep right there
like that, love!

06:57.984 --> 07:00.285
Oi, mate!
Get off set, you galah!

07:00.320 --> 07:01.553
Oh!
- Don't go!

07:01.588 --> 07:02.754
It's okay, it's okay.

07:02.789 --> 07:04.289
I'll be right here
the whole time.

07:04.324 --> 07:05.290
Looking great, love!

07:05.325 --> 07:06.958
All right, Corgis,
take your marks.

07:06.993 --> 07:09.494
♪ Orange eggplant ♪

07:09.529 --> 07:11.262
♪ Corgi party ♪

07:11.297 --> 07:13.264
♪ Purple bacon ♪

07:13.299 --> 07:15.834
♪ Corgi party ♪

07:15.869 --> 07:18.803
And...cut!
You beauty! We got it!

07:18.838 --> 07:20.472
Let's take a ten-minute break,
everybody.

07:20.507 --> 07:22.640
Then it's just one more take,
and we're done.

07:22.675 --> 07:25.210
[ Sighs ] Nailed it.

07:26.713 --> 07:27.946
It's all just too easy.

07:27.981 --> 07:29.647
[ Knock at door ]
Come in!

07:29.682 --> 07:31.015
Nom Nom!
That was amazing!

07:31.050 --> 07:33.618
You didn't yell, you didn't
bite, nobody's crying!

07:33.653 --> 07:35.119
I'm not crying!
You've done it!

07:35.154 --> 07:37.121
Yep, so long as this guy
is next to me,

07:37.156 --> 07:39.591
everything is smooth sailing.

07:39.626 --> 07:41.025
Glad to be useful!

07:41.060 --> 07:43.094
Grizzly: So it's like you're
a good person now.

07:43.129 --> 07:44.963
This is fantastic!
We should tol--

07:44.998 --> 07:47.499
[ Gasps ] It's -- It's --
It's the kangaroo!

07:47.534 --> 07:49.534
[ French accent ]
<i>Quoi?</i> What is it?

07:49.569 --> 07:52.136
It's really you!
I love your work so much!

07:52.171 --> 07:53.805
I'm --
I'm friends with Nom Nom.

07:53.840 --> 07:55.139
Wait, look --
I'm wearing you!

07:55.174 --> 07:56.774
Sign it! Please!
Sign the back!

07:56.809 --> 07:59.277
Oh, don't touch me!

07:59.312 --> 08:02.547
Mmm? It looks like you could
use one of my special hugs.

08:02.582 --> 08:04.015
Security!

08:04.050 --> 08:06.784
Whoa!

08:06.819 --> 08:07.986
Ah! Nom Nom!

08:08.021 --> 08:10.154
Let me in!
Let me in!

08:10.189 --> 08:12.490
This is bad.

08:12.525 --> 08:15.827
All right, mates, for this
last one, more intensity!

08:15.862 --> 08:17.328
Okay, mate!

08:17.363 --> 08:20.064
Wait, more intense?
What more is needed?

08:20.099 --> 08:22.000
I think not only do
we need more smiles,

08:22.035 --> 08:24.669
but also more sunshine!

08:24.704 --> 08:26.838
And rainbows
for that smile!

08:26.873 --> 08:30.008
Uh, anybody seen the bear?

08:31.344 --> 08:33.177
Oh! Excuse me, sir!
You have to let me in!

08:33.212 --> 08:34.846
I need
to go help my buddy.

08:34.881 --> 08:37.248
You can't go inside unless you
work on that kid's clown show.

08:37.283 --> 08:40.485
Oh, I totally work
on the clown show.

08:40.520 --> 08:42.186
♪ Doot do do doot do
doot do doot ♪

08:42.221 --> 08:44.155
♪ Doot do do doot doot ♪

08:44.190 --> 08:46.491
Okay, well then lets get you
into makeup first.

08:46.526 --> 08:47.859
♪ Party ♪

08:47.894 --> 08:49.694
♪ Red pineapple ♪

08:49.729 --> 08:51.563
♪ Corgi party ♪

08:51.598 --> 08:53.398
♪ Blue banana ♪

08:53.433 --> 08:55.066
♪ Corgi party ♪

08:55.101 --> 08:57.035
♪ Orange eggplant ♪

08:57.070 --> 08:58.870
♪ Corgi party ♪

08:58.905 --> 09:00.705
♪ Purple bacon ♪

09:00.740 --> 09:02.240
♪ Corgi party ♪

09:02.275 --> 09:03.942
[ Growling ]
♪ It's a Corgi pa-- ♪

09:03.977 --> 09:06.511
All righty, well,
let's get you in there.

09:06.546 --> 09:10.014
♪ So much fun... ♪
Oh! Oh, no, Nom Nom!

09:10.049 --> 09:12.050
♪ It's really, really fun ♪

09:12.085 --> 09:15.353
[ Gasps ] Hold on, buddy,
I'm coming!

09:15.388 --> 09:17.689
[ Panting ]

09:17.724 --> 09:20.024
[ Distorted ] ♪ Green sandwich ♪

09:20.059 --> 09:22.560
♪ Corgi party ♪

09:22.595 --> 09:25.630
♪ Red pineapple ♪

09:25.665 --> 09:28.866
♪ Corgi party ♪

09:28.901 --> 09:31.736
Out of the way,
out of the way, gah!

09:31.771 --> 09:33.805
Aah...

09:33.840 --> 09:35.807
Gah!

09:35.842 --> 09:37.942
[ Muffled screams ]

09:37.977 --> 09:42.013
Aah! Aah! Aah! Aah! Aah!

09:45.451 --> 09:47.385
Is he still kickin'?

09:47.420 --> 09:50.421
I feel just peachy!
[ Laughs ]

09:50.456 --> 09:51.823
[ Cheering ]

09:51.858 --> 09:54.225
[ Both sigh ]

09:54.260 --> 09:57.729
♪ Just hug your friend
and say whoo-hoo ♪

09:57.764 --> 09:59.731
And, cut!

09:59.766 --> 10:02.300
You beauty! We got it!
Bonza!

10:02.335 --> 10:03.901
-Let's go home!
-[ Sighs ]

10:03.936 --> 10:05.603
Good on ya, Noms,
you little legend!

10:05.638 --> 10:08.139
It'd be a real treat to work
together again, mate!

10:08.174 --> 10:10.441
You're a cool little
critter, Noms!

10:10.476 --> 10:12.310
On ya, spirit!

10:12.345 --> 10:13.978
Congratulations,
Nom Nom.

10:14.013 --> 10:16.114
Your popularity is
on the rise again!

10:16.149 --> 10:18.416
Andy bangs is eating your dust!
He's totally over!

10:18.451 --> 10:20.084
And your mansion
has doubled.

10:20.119 --> 10:21.419
All in a day's work.

10:21.454 --> 10:23.421
Let's head home.
- You did it!

10:23.456 --> 10:25.423
Oh, you were perfect,
I'm so proud of you.

10:25.458 --> 10:27.792
So what's the next gig?
Where are we going now?

10:27.827 --> 10:29.327
Yeah, um, you know,

10:29.362 --> 10:31.462
I don't think we should
keep this thing going.

10:31.497 --> 10:34.265
Oh. Um, okay.

10:34.300 --> 10:36.334
But -- But what
about your anger?

10:36.369 --> 10:39.604
Eh, I'm rich and famous,
I'll figure something out.

10:39.639 --> 10:42.974
So, uh...see ya!

10:43.009 --> 10:46.011
Hey, man, how about one
for the road?

10:50.216 --> 10:53.951
Okay, put me down.

10:53.986 --> 10:56.254
Hey,
this never happened.

10:58.691 --> 11:00.158
[ Door slams ]
Huh.

11:00.193 --> 11:02.494
I think that was my ride home.

11:04.597 --> 11:06.665
♪♪
